Reasoning: The paper deals with exact Ramsey theory and SAT solving, which are both topics in discrete mathematics (cs.DM). The use of SAT solvers also falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and circuit complexity (cs.CC). The paper also discusses the translation of non-boolean clause-sets to boolean clause-sets, which is a topic in logic (cs.LO) and data structures (cs.DS).
